column5: Hi all...I have been browsing the site for some time now, and figured it was to introduce myself...I am Kyle from hamilton...I do most of my fishing on whitestone lake but also enjoy fishing local spots such as mounstberg and niapenco...anyways, looking forward to continuing to learn from you all, and hope I can contribute myself a bit
Welcome to OFC Kyle Looking forward to reading your future reports!!! Leechman

Welcome Aboard Kyle ....Im not from Hamilton but been working in Stoney Creek for the last week and this week comming ....i now have a new found respect for the area because of the heritage and natural wonders of the escarpment ....really cool....
welcome aboard...  fyi,,, we like reports with pics
